        {
            "title": "缺德遊客抓海鷗拍照 雲南撫仙湖管理局：已違法｜有片",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<div id=\"vdo-player-container\">\n<video class=\"video-js vjs-default-skin\" controls=\"\" id=\"vdo-player\" muted=\"\" playsinline=\"\" poster=\"\" width=\"100%\">\n<source src=\"https://video.hkhl.hk/6009219c00a571f086444177d1c00102/1143d7dccc73492c8ad4f7a636633b79-3acd4d5b7967de39794fe6c2e009ae90-ld.mp4\" type=\"video/mp4\">\n                        Your browser does not support the video tag.\n                    </source></video>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container web\" data-vslot=\"vod_ad\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67d3e7a310fab\"></div>\n<div class=\"vdo-ad-container mweb\" data-vslot0=\"vod_ad,2\" id=\"div-gpt-vad-67d3e7a310fad\"></div>\n</div>\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"雲南撫仙湖有遊客輪流抓著海鷗拍照。新京報\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/d72407d69c923ccfb4c61ad5fe00856b/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250314/_2025031416220148888.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">雲南撫仙湖有遊客輪流抓著海鷗拍照。新京報</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>3月13日，雲南玉溪撫仙湖有遊客輪流抓著海鷗拍照。網上視頻顯示，一名男子抓著海鷗讓同伴拍完照後，再將海鷗交給另一名女子繼續拍照。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3431162/%E7%96%91%E4%BC%BC%E5%8F%B0%E7%81%A3%E4%BA%BA%E6%8D%89%E5%BC%84%E5%A5%88%E8%89%AF%E9%B9%BF-%E6%97%A5%E4%BA%BA%E6%80%92%E6%96%A5%E5%88%A5%E5%86%8D%E4%BE%86%E4%BA%86\">疑似台灣人捉弄奈良鹿 日人怒斥：別再來了</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"雲南撫仙湖有遊客輪流抓著海鷗拍照。新京報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/76fdd962448017328934bfe738d710ac/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1415_30_39_6f5833ac.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雲南撫仙湖有遊客輪流抓著海鷗拍照。新京報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"雲南撫仙湖有遊客輪流抓著海鷗拍照。新京報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/83143ef759bbabf9f2f04dcd5f5824d3/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1415_30_39_5379ffec.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雲南撫仙湖有遊客輪流抓著海鷗拍照。新京報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"雲南撫仙湖有遊客輪流抓著海鷗拍照。新京報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d6acc08dd7023fdd288966027274847d/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1415_30_40_c7fa12e3.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雲南撫仙湖有遊客輪流抓著海鷗拍照。新京報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"雲南撫仙湖有遊客輪流抓著海鷗拍照。新京報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/9474c4b04d612e9faab1696f93ef7869/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1415_30_40_d8ab97af.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雲南撫仙湖有遊客輪流抓著海鷗拍照。新京報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"雲南撫仙湖有遊客輪流抓著海鷗拍照。新京報\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/95634412eb4eb35187c5e1a7f4fe492a/2025-03/WhatsApp_2025-03-1415_30_40_f147240b.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        雲南撫仙湖有遊客輪流抓著海鷗拍照。新京報\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"撫仙湖是雲南著名景點。新華社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/a17c80734118770c374ac58a1168cd2d/2025-03/XxjpsgC007286_20250112_PEPFN0A001.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        撫仙湖是雲南著名景點。新華社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"撫仙湖是雲南著名景點。新華社\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/10ea3c909db2a38cc121e0f32c5e9f14/2025-03/XxjpsgC007285_20250112_PEPFN0A001.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        撫仙湖是雲南著名景點。新華社\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>據新京報報道，14日，撫仙湖管理局回應指，已接到舉報視頻，將聯繫遊客進行處理。捕捉海鷗拍照是違法的行為，工作人員巡查中發現此類情況將及時制止，並對遊客進行普法。此外，投食海鷗會降低其捕食能力，還可能造成水體污染。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-china/3436980/%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E6%B3%95%E6%BA%90%E5%AF%BA600%E5%B9%B4%E7%9F%B3%E7%8D%85%E5%AD%90-%E9%81%AD%E7%BC%BA%E5%BE%B7%E9%81%8A%E5%AE%A2%E5%88%BB%E6%84%8F%E6%8E%A8%E5%80%92-%E8%BA%AB%E9%A6%96%E7%95%B0%E8%99%95%E6%9C%89%E7%89%87\">北京法源寺600年石獅子 遭缺德遊客刻意推倒 身首異處｜有片</a>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://std.stheadline.com/realtime/article/2058166/即時-中國-缺德遊客抓海鷗拍照-雲南撫仙湖管理局-已違法-有片",
