            "title": "姜濤 陳卓賢Ian成萌爆港產熊貓星級契爸 4月出席「家姐細佬後援會成立典禮」",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"姜濤 陳卓賢成萌爆港產熊貓星級契爸 4月出席「家姐細佬後援會成立典禮」\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/fa3a1bfc76cb344385d103a39c59fe07/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250314/_2025031415343258990.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">姜濤 陳卓賢成萌爆港產熊貓星級契爸 4月出席「家姐細佬後援會成立典禮」</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>一對萌爆港產大熊貓寶寶號召各位粉絲加入海洋公園全新成立的「家姐細佬後援會」，成為「家姐」、「細佬」最親密的「契爸契媽」，而兩位星級「契爸」、MIRROR成員陳卓賢（Ian）及姜濤預告於4月18日出席「家姐細佬後援會成立典禮」，及率先現身「星級契爸獨家團」。\n\n</p><h2>姜濤 陳卓賢4月現身</h2>\n<p>即日起至4月8日前加入後援會，即可參加入場券大抽獎，600名幸運兒將可獲入場券一張，與Ian、姜濤齊齊為一對至萌孖寶送上滿滿祝福；同時擁有「海洋公園全年會籍」的「家姐細佬後援會」會員，可於即日起至2025年4月8日期間參加「星級契爸獨家團」大抽獎。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4137149/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"姜濤、陳卓賢成萌爆港產熊貓寶寶的星級契爸。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/84fe46b02cc13a916f89fdab9ba5fdac/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-14_at_15_01_45_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        姜濤、陳卓賢成萌爆港產熊貓寶寶的星級契爸。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4137150/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"陳卓賢、姜濤於4月出席「家姐細佬後援會成立典禮」。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/1a8474a59b53d4a2f9cbfbda02b49937/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-14_at_15_01_45_2_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        陳卓賢、姜濤於4月出席「家姐細佬後援會成立典禮」。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4137151/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"兩隻港產熊貓寶寶好cute！\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8410dc8a46a4d2f8ac73997c22574c15/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-14_at_15_01_45_3_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        兩隻港產熊貓寶寶好cute！\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4137152/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"姜濤、陳卓賢與熊貓紀念品合照。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bc796f1af3f76f7364ddec8651a298a1/2025-03/WhatsApp_Image_2025-03-14_at_15_01_45.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        姜濤、陳卓賢與熊貓紀念品合照。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail fie